Carlos WILSON, petitioner,

No. 17-8746.

Oct. 15, 2018.
Petition for writ of certiorari to the United States Court of Appeals for the Eleventh Circuit denied.
Justice SOTOMAYOR, dissenting form the denial of certiorari: I dissent from the denial of certiorari for the reasons set out in Brown v. United States, 586 U.S. ----, 139 S.Ct. 14, --- L.E.2d ---- (2018) ( Sotomayor, J., dissenting).
